      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Our novel package rawrr now provides complete, OS-independent access to all spectral data logged in Thermo Fisher Scientific raw files... This use case shows how easy it is to perform iRT regression in R by just using the raw measurement data, our package rawrr, and well-known base R functions supporting linear modeling.",
