      "asbval:target_claim_field": "research_question",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Fit a linear regression model to retention time (RT) data extracted from liquid chromatography\u2013mass spectrometry (LC-MS) runs using calibrant peptides (e.g., iRT standards) to quantify the linearity of RT behavior and validate chromatographic reproducibility.",
