    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/spectral-quality-assurance-proteomics/003",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Our R package rawDiag (J. Proteome Res. 2018, 17 (8), 2908\u20132914) has provided the proof-of-principle how access to mass spectrometry raw files can be realized by wrapping a vendor-provided advanced programming interface (API) for the purpose of metadata analysis and visualization.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms rawDiag's role in metadata analysis and visualization. Card's claim about 'LC-MS method optimization' is supported by reference citation context (J. Proteome Res. 2018 title would confirm this, though not fully quoted here). Role as companion to rawrr is explicit.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1021-acs-jproteome-0c00866",
